public abstract class AbstractDlProcessTest
extends org.springframework.test.context.junit4.AbstractJUnit4SpringContextTests

Description: The purpose of this class is to encapsulate the behavior of running junits with spring configuration for business processes. All the junits for business processes should extend this class. Before running junits that extend this class, start a local instance of WAS configured with the latest EASE CAR file. The superclass AbstractJUnit4SpringContextTests is not compatible with junit 4.5. Use junit 4.4 or 4.6 or later.
